    ns1:learningResultDescription "Be able to sketch a project for the development of an intelligent virtual environment, establishing the process to be followed, the technologies to be used, the interaction possibilities to offer, and the role to be played by intelligent virtual agents, selecting the most appropriate technologies, architectures and tools for the development."@es .

